title: Chanel Vintage Top CC Kisslock Shoulder Bag
description: Chanel vintage Top CC kisslock bag in black diamond-quilted lambskin (#4xxxxxx). Featuring gold-tone hardware, classic CC stitched logo on the base, & dual leather-woven chain shoulder straps. The top CC turn-lock closure opens to a black leather interior with a patch pocket & zip pocket. Approx. dimensions: 31cm(B-L) x 21.5cm(H) x 12.5cm(D), 28cm shoulder drop. Accompanied by Chanel card, booklet, dustbag & box. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
